<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Restablecer Contraseña</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            color-scheme: light;
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            /* Estilos para el modo oscuro */
            body {
                background-color: #fff;
                color: black;
            }
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {
            /* Estilos para el modo claro */
            body {
                background-color: #fff;
                color: black;
            }
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #808285;
        }

        a {
            color: 'inherit';
        }

        .background-container {
            width: 100%;
            background-size: 100% 100%;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: bottom center;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
        }

        .card-container {
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            background: transparent;
            padding: 20px 35px;
            margin: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Media Query para dispositivos móviles */

        @media (max-width: 767px) {
            .card-container {
                max-width: 80%;
            }
        }

        /* Media Query para dispositivos con un ancho mayor a 767px (cambia según tus necesidades) */

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .card-container {
                width: 600px;
            }
        }

        .card-body-mail {
            background: url('https://viabo.com/production_images/success-2x.png');
            background-size: 40%;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: top 30px right 0px;
        }

        .inner-card {
            background-image: url('https://viabo.com/production_images/white_bg.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center center;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            max-width: 100%;
            margin: auto;
            position: relative;
        }

        .logo {
            height: 27px;
            width: auto;
            margin-right: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #02539e;
            text-align: left;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .text {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #808285;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #5C34F5;
            color: 'white' !important;
            border: none;
            padding: 7px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: justify;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer p {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #808285;
        }

        .footer hr {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid #808285;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .subtitle {
            max-width: 70%;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #808285;
        }

        .footer-table {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #808285;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }

        .details-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-top: 25px;
            color: #02539e;
        }

        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .details-table tr td {
            padding: 8px 0px;
            margin: 0px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #D0D0D0;
        }

        .details-table tr td:first-child {
            color: #808285;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 20px 20px;
            background-color: #02539e;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            width: 200px;
            border: none;
            text-align: center
        }

        .purple {
            color: #02539e;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
    </style>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
<div class="background-container">
    <div class="card-container">
        <div class="inner-card">
            <div class="card-body-mail">
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <img src="https://viabo.com/production_images/set/set_logo.png" alt="SET logo"
                     class="logo">
                        </td>

                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <h1 class="title">¡Hola {{ name }}!</h1>
                            <p class="subtitle">Te informamos que se ha solicitado el restablecimiento de tu
                                contraseña:</p>
                            <p class="details-title">Credenciales:</p>
                            <table class="details-table">
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="color:black!important;">Usuario:</td>
                                    <td class="purple">{{ userEmail }}</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="color:black!important;">Contraseña:</td>
                                    <td class="purple">{{ password }}</td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </td>

                    </tr>
                </table>

                <a href="{{ host }}" class="btn-primary" style="color:white!important;">Iniciar Sesión</a>
                <hr style="margin-top:50px">
                <p class="footer-table">Gracias por no responder este correo.<br>Dudas o aclaraciones dirigirse al área
                    correspondiente de la empresa.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>

</html>
